result.name: 2016-2016-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-dplus0045-anguilla-still-i
result.notes:
Still image analysis of the groundtruthing data collected as part of the 
Darwin Plus funded project "Mapping Anguilla’s ‘Blue Belt’ Ecosystem 
Services". The project develops local capacity to undertake comprehensive 
marine resource assessments of Anguilla’s ‘Blue-Belt’, delivering best 
practice guidance for combining satellite and acoustic surveys, to extend 
mapping into deeper waters for the first time.
